/www.healthaffairs.org/do/10.1377/hblog20171022.713615/full/">https://www.healthaffairs.org/do/10.1377/hblog20171022.713615/full/</a>.</div><div class="div article_references-links cat-body4"><a href="/servlet/linkout?suffix=e_1_3_2_4_2&amp;dbid=16&amp;doi=10.1056%2FCAT.20.0093&amp;key=10.1377%2Fhblog20171022.713615" onclick="newWindow(this.href);return false" target="_blank">Crossref</a><span class="references__suffix">, <a class="google-scholar" href="http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=Huilgol+YS%2C+Joshi+A%2C+Carr+BG%2C+Hollander+JE.+Giving+urban+health+care+access+issues+the+attention+they+deserve+in+telemedicine+reimbursement+policies.+Health+Affairs+Blog.+October+12%2C+2017.+Accessed+March+26%2C+2020.+10.1377%2Fhblog20171022.713615https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthaffairs.org%2Fdo%2F10.1377%2Fhblog20171022.713615%2Ffull%2F."target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></span></div></div></li><li id="r4" class="&#xA;                references__item&#xA;            "><div class="article_references-num">4</div><div class="article_references-content"><div class="article_references-text">Handley N, Hollander JE. Opportunity cost: the hidden toll of seeking health care. Health Affairs Blog. May 1, 2019. Accessed March 26, 2020. <span class="references__pub-id">10.1377/hblog20190429.592190.</span> <a class="references__uri article_new-window-link" href="https://www.healthaffairs.org/do/10.1377/hblog20190429.592190/full/">https://www.healthaffairs.org/do/10.1377/hblog20190429.592190/full/</a>.</div><div class="div article_references-links cat-body4"><a href="/servlet/linkout?suffix=e_1_3_2_5_2&amp;dbid=16&amp;doi=10.1056%2FCAT.20.0093&amp;key=10.1377%2Fhblog20190429.592190" onclick="newWindow(this.href);return false" target="_blank">Crossref</a><span class="references__suffix">, <a class="google-scholar" href="http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=Handley+N%2C+Hollander+JE.+Opportunity+cost%3A+the+hidden+toll+of+seeking+health+care.+Health+Affairs+Blog.+May+1%2C+2019.+Accessed+March+26%2C+2020.+10.1377%2Fhblog20190429.592190https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthaffairs.org%2Fdo%2F10.1377%2Fhblog20190429.592190%2Ffull%2F."target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></span></div></div></li><li id="r5" class="&#xA;                references__item&#xA;            "><div class="article_references-num">5</div><div class="article_references-content"><div class="article_references-text"><span class="person-group">TH Lee</span>. <span class="references__article-title">Creating the New Normal: The Clinician Response to Covid-19.</span><span class="references__source">NEJM Catalyst</span><span class="references__year">2020</span>; 1 <a class="references__uri article_new-window-link" href="https://catalyst.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/CAT.20.0076">https://catalyst.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/CAT.20.0076</a> Accessed March 26, 2020.</div><div class="div article_references-links cat-body4"><span class="references__suffix"><a class="google-scholar" href="http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=LeeTH.+Creating+the+New+Normal%3A+The+Clinician+Response+to+Covid-19.NEJM+Catalyst2020%3B1https%3A%2F%2Fcatalyst.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FCAT.20.0076+Accessed+March+26%2C+2020."target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></span></div></div></li></ul></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="pb-dropzone" data-pb-dropzone="topicsDropzone"><div class="topic-tags"><span>Topics</span><ul><li><a href="/topic/topics/patient-experience">Patient Experience</a></li><li><a href="/topic/topics/care-management">Care Management</a></li><li><a href="/topic/topics/disruption-and-innovation">Disruption and Innovation</a></li><li><a href="/topic/topics/electronic-health-records">Electronic Health Records</a></li><li><a href="/topic/topics/digital-health">Digital Health</a></li><li><a href="/topic/topics/specialty-care">Specialty Care</a></li><li><a href="/topic/topics/primary-care">Primary Care</a></li></ul></div></div></div><!--/fulltext content--></div><div class="article_content_center"></div><div clas